---
title: Candy | Home
layout: layouts/base.njk
bodyClass: candy-page
templateEngineOverride: njk, md
contentContainerClass: container-fluid
---
<div class="row justify-content-end parallax-window">
  <div class="col-6 col-lg-5 pr-5">
    <h1 class="super-title">Candy</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      <span class="candy-logo">Candy</span> is an Eleventy project starter with loads of sugar on top. Sweet extras like ...<br>
      <span class="txt-rotate" data-period="1000" data-rotate='[ "Bootstrap 4.", "Gulp.", "Sass.", "Custom Widgets.", "jQuery.", "PrismJS.", "Google Fonts.", "Custom Filters.", "SEO Optimizations." ]'>Bootstrap 4, Gulp, Sass, PrismJS, and more!</span>
      <span class="txt-rotate-space">&nbsp;</span>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row deploy-netflify-row p-3 justify-content-center">
  <div class="col-12 col-md-7 col-lg-6">
    <div>Get your own clone of Eleventy + <span class="candy-logo">Candy</span> deployed to <a href="https://www.netlify.com">Netlify</a>! Click the <i>Deploy to Netlify</i> button and follow the instructions.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-12 col-md-5 col-lg-3">
    <p><a href="https://app.netlify.com/start/deploy?repository=https://github.com/stickhandle/eleventy-candy"><img class="netlify-button" src="https://www.netlify.com/img/deploy/button.svg" alt="Deploy to Netlify"></a></p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container mt-3">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="card-deck">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header center">
          <h4 class="card-title"><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Delicious Build Pipeline</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>&nbsp;Yarn&nbsp;<i class="fab fa-yarn"></i> for dependencies.<br></p>
          <p class="card-text"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>&nbsp;Gulp&nbsp;<i class="fab fa-gulp"></i> build pipeline with preprocessing of images, CSS and JS.</p>
          <p class="card-text"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>&nbsp;Nunjucks templates.</p>
          <p class="card-text"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>&nbsp;Markdown-it&nbsp;<i class="fab fa-markdown"></i> for content + footnote and emoji support.</p>
          <p class="card-text"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>&nbsp;11ty pulls it all together.<br></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header center">
          <h4 class="card-title"><i class="fas fa-desktop"></i> Yummy Display Goodies</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>&nbsp;Sass&nbsp;<i class="fab fa-sass"></i> for sassy CSS preprocessing.</p>
          <p class="card-text"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>&nbsp;Bootstrap responsive component library baked in.</p>
          <p class="card-text"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>&nbsp;jQuery ready.</p>
          <p class="card-text"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>&nbsp;PrismJS for syntax highlighting.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header center">
          <h4 class="card-title">üç≠ Candy Custom Treats</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>&nbsp;Blog and Portfolio ready.</p>
          <p class="card-text"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>&nbsp;Custom Related Posts and Favorites widgets.</p>
          <p class="card-text"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>&nbsp;Custom Tags page.</p>
          <p class="card-text"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>&nbsp;Custom filters.</p>
          <p class="card-text"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>&nbsp;Ready for RSS.</p>
          <p class="card-text"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>&nbsp;SEO Optimizations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>  
<div class="row">
  <div class="col">
    <blockquote cite="Charles Schulz">All I really need is love, but a little candy now and then doesn't hurt!</blockquote>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col"><h3>Latest from the Blog ...</h3></div>
  </div>
  {%- set cls = cycler("odd", "even") -%}
  {%- for post in collections.posts.slice(0, 3) %}
    <div class="blog-list-item h3-to-mini {{ cls.next() }}">
        <div class="row">
            {% if post.data.mainImageFilename -%}
                {% if cls.current == 'odd' -%}
                    {% include "blog-item-odd.njk" -%}
                {% else -%}
                    {% include "blog-item-even.njk" -%}
                {% endif -%}
            {% else -%}
                {% include "blog-item-noimage.njk" -%}
            {% endif -%}
        </div>
    </div>
  {%- endfor %}
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col">
    <blockquote class="bq-dark" cite="Scott Adams">You don't argue with a four-year old about why he shouldn't eat candy for dinner.</blockquote>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col"><h3>Latest from the Portfolio ...</h3></div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    {%- set cls = cycler("cycle-item-a", "cycle-item-b", "cycle-item-b", "cycle-item-a") -%}
    {%- for photo in collections.photos.slice(0, 4) %}
        <div class="col-6 col-lg-3 {{ cls.next() }}">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <div class="mini-h3"><a class="title-href" href="{{ photo.url }}">{{ photo.data.title }}</a></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col postline">
                        <div class="postdate" style="margin-left: 0px">
                            <i class="fas fa-calendar-day"></i>
                            <div>{{ photo.date | formatDisplayDate }}</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {%- if not photo.data.mainImageTitle  -%}
                    {% set mainImageTitle = photo.data.mainImageFilename %}
                {%- else -%}
                    {% set mainImageTitle = photo.data.mainImageTitle %}
                {%- endif -%}
                {%- if not photo.data.mainImageAltText  -%}
                    {% set mainImageAltText = mainImageTitle %}
                {%- else -%}
                    {% set mainImageAltText = photo.data.mainImageAltText %}
                {%- endif -%}
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col main-image">
                        <a href="{{ photo.url }}">
                            <img src="/images/{{ photo.data.mainImageFilename }}-{{ photo.data.thumbImageSize }}.{{ photo.data.mainImageExt }}" alt="{{ mainImageAltText | safe }}" title="{{ mainImageTitle | safe }}">
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col postline">
                        <div class="tags">
                            {% for tag in photo.data.tags -%}
                                {% if tag != "untagged" -%}
                                    {% if loop.first %}<i class="fas fa-tags"></i>{% endif -%}
                                    <div><a href="/tags/#{{ tag }}" class="tag">#{{ tag }}</a></div>
                                {% endif -%}
                            {% endfor -%}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
        </div>
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>
</div>





